contentrichtext.text: '''Adamstown''' may refer to one of the following places: ; Australia: * [[Adamstown, New South Wales]], a town in New South Wales ; Ireland: * [[Adamstown, County Wexford]], a village in County Wexford * [[Adamstown, Dublin]], an urban village in County Dublin ; Pitcairn Island (UK possession, Oceania): * [[Adamstown, Pitcairn Islands]], the capital city of the Pitcairn Islands ; United States: * Adamstown, alternate name for [[Neals Diggins, California]] * [[Adamstown Township, Maine]] * [[Adamstown, Maryland]], a town in Frederick County, Maryland * [[Adamstown, Pennsylvania]], a borough in Lancaster County, Pennsylvania {{geodis}}
